OL,4,CFormer ITV boss Adam Crozier appointed
OL,5,Cnew chairman of BT
OL,6, The former boss of Royal Mail, ITV and
OL,7, the Football Association, Adam Crozier,
OL,8, is to become the new chairman of BT.
OL,10,FMr Crozier will succeed retiring
OL,11,Fchairman Jan du Plessis and will join
OL,12,Fthe telecoms giant's board in November,
OL,13,Fthe company announced.
OL,15,FBT said the incoming boss had "built a
OL,16,Fstrong track record in turning around
OL,17,Forganisations".
OL,19,FHe joins the company as it looks to
OL,20,Fspeed up its roll out of full-fibre
OL,21,Fbroadband to 25 million homes by 2026.
